                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On October 24 President <persName corresp="#p_THS1">Truman</persName> proclaimed
                    that the state of war between the United States and the Government of Germany
                    had been terminated on October 19. For the text of the proclamation, see <hi
                        rend="italic">American Foreign Policy, 1950–1955: Basic Documents</hi>,
                    volume II, pages 1723–1724, or 66 Stat. c3.</p>
            </div>
